<br>
I know what your saying but that is what caster balance is supposed to be for - and yes, I am being a bit presumptuous - but that is what I got out of the letter when it was announced.<br>
<br>
In the end I may be wrong about the caster balance, but I do feel that 1 spell each class, such as eldricks for wizards, Mask for druids, mark for clerics and so on is not the end of the world and something I can certainly live with. As for me having mask for all those wondering.. the answer is no, shoot I don't even have Greater Remove Curse or Enduring Breath, Japanese and European guilds are owning those spawns atm, but in time I will eventual get it. - <br>
<br>
Good discussion by the way - I respect your views in this manner - and who knows I may change my mind if Caster Balance isn't as well done as Melee Balance was.<br>
